Entity:
User:
Id,name,surname,username(unique),age, password
Relation: one-to-many with Announcement
Announcement:
Id, viewCount
Relation: one-to-one with AnnDetail
AnnouncementDetail:
Id,title,description,price,createDate,updateDate
API:
Public:
/login
/getAllAnnouncements with specification
/getMostViewedAnnouncements**
Private:
/createAnnouncement
/updateAnnouncement
/deleteAnnouncement
/getAllOwnAnnouncement
/getOwnAnnouncementWithId
/getOwnMostViewedAnnouncement
Login olmani username, password-e gore qurarsiz. Login olmush useri User table-da nezere alarsiz.
